{
  "stem": "27390.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after we had enough coupons, so we went along to this office from this coffee firm to exchange these labels-- these coupons to get the album with the labels.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this-- the office was already outside the Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no more Jews living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came near this office, some Polish boys around the same age as us started throwing stones at us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we ran very fast away till we came back into the Jewish quarter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when I realized the first time that I'm a Jew and I'm being treated different, even by children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did they see you were Jewish?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they could tell the way we were dressed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to have caps, different caps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Polish schools had different caps to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We, we had-- they could tell we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, the attitude in Poland, it's hard to understand today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were told on Sunday when we were on holiday-- we didn't notice it so much in town, but when we were on holiday-- we lived in the village, which was surrounded by Poles-- and we were told not to go out on Sunday at the time when the people come out from the churches.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the-- the-- the church used to whip up the-- the Poles against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they came out, they started beating up Jews, whoever was around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were always told not to go out at that time, when the people come out from the churches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, it was normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they used to-- they used to come out from the church and they-- whoever was in the-- whoever was about was beaten up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It happened very often.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They could tell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could tell.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
